This paper focuses on deep neural networks for object detection, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of collaborative intelligence, which involves communication between mobile devices and the cloud, and lossy compression of feature data. These topics are relevant to machine learning (cs.LG), multimedia (cs.MM), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and distributed computing (cs.DC).
